#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&marble; is a geographical atlas and a virtual globe which lets you quickly "
"explore places on our home planet. You can use &marble; to look up "
"addresses, to easily create maps, measure distances and to retrieve detail "
"information about locations that you have just heard about in the news or on "
"the Internet. The user interface is clean, simple and easy to use."
msgstr ""
"&marble; je geografski atlas i virtualni globus koji brzo otvara mjesta na "
"našoj planeti. Možeš korititi &marble; za traženje adresa, lahko kreirati "
"mape, napraviti distance i povratiti detaljne  informacije o lokacijama o "
"kojima si upravo čuo u vijestima ili na internetu. Korisnički međuodnos je "
"čist, jednostavan i lagan za koristiti."

