msgstr "Pronađite vaš način sa &marble;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Besides searching for places, &marble; can display possible routes "
#| "between two or more of them. Do you want to plan a bicycle tour in the "
